sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Notebook
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant Webhook as Webhook Service<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+ mTLS
    participant Controller as RayCluster Controller
    participant RouteAPI as Route API (OpenShift)<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OAuthProxy as OAuth Proxy via Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant RayDash as Ray Dashboard<br/>8265/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,RayDash: Flow 1: RayCluster Creation with OAuth (OpenShift)

    User->>K8sAPI: POST RayCluster CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (ServiceAccount)
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate/Mutate RayCluster<br/>mTLS (API Server cert)
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation Response
    K8sAPI-->>User: Created

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch RayCluster<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Controller->>RouteAPI: Create Route for Dashboard<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Service<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy<br/>Auth: Bearer Token

    User->>OAuthProxy: Access Ray Dashboard<br/>Auth: OAuth Bearer Token
    OAuthProxy->>RayDash: Forward request<br/>HTTP (internal pod)
    RayDash-->>OAuthProxy: Dashboard HTML
    OAuthProxy-->>User: Dashboard Response
